#: TWLight/users/templates/users/editor_detail.html:40
msgid "Both historical and current, made to various partners"
msgstr "Historické aj aktuálne, podané rôznym partnerom"

#. Translators: This is the heading for user information on profile and application pages.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/editor_detail.html:47
